# - Team handles should be in the form @org/team-name (example: @gradeloop/backend-team).
# - Usernames are in the form @username.
#
# Notes:
# - Patterns are matched from top to bottom; most-specific patterns should appear first.
# - See GitHub docs for advanced pattern details: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
